You know that I am a fan, since I am a member of your channell, so I hope you will interpret my input as something helpful, the way it is intended:

Your microphone picks up way too much background noise, to the detriment of your lovely guests. 

I hope you will be able to do something about this situation, even if it is only muting yourself while the others talk. There are a few moments towards the end of the conversation where we suddenly hear Jackie and Zod clear as crystal, which makes all the crackling and cutting in and out before even more sad.

Please keep up all the great work, and let's have even more streams with good sound quality! :)
